### Permitted Use

Users may use this dataset for non-commercial purposes.

Users may share and redistribute this dataset online or offline for non-commercial purposes.

Users may modify, process, transform, and create derivative works based on this dataset for non-commercial purposes.

All permitted uses are allowed only when the license conditions described in this document are satisfied.

### License Conditions

#### 1. Attribution

Users must indicate the source or copyright holder when using this dataset.

A recommended attribution format is:

> This work uses the "[Dataset Name]" dataset, created by [Institution Name] in [Year] and released under KOGL Type 2. The dataset is available from [Distribution Site or URL].

When an online hyperlink to the source website is available, users should provide the link.

Attribution must not imply that the providing institution endorses the user or that the user has a special relationship with the providing institution.

#### 2. Non-Commercial Use Only

This dataset may be used only for non-commercial purposes.

Users may not use this dataset for activities that are directly or indirectly related to commercial or profit-making purposes.

Commercial use may be permitted only when separate permission is obtained from the right holder or the providing institution.

#### 3. Respect for Moral Rights

When modifying, processing, transforming, or creating derivative works from this dataset, users must respect the moral rights of the original author or right holder.

Users must not use this dataset in a way that damages the honor or reputation of the original author or materially distorts the meaning of the original work.

#### 4. Compliance with Laws and Third-Party Rights

This license does not replace permissions required under applicable laws or permissions required from third-party right holders.

If the dataset contains information subject to separate legal restrictions or third-party rights, including personal information, credit information, military secrets, copyrights, trademarks, design rights, or patent rights, users must comply with the applicable laws and permission requirements.

#### 5. Disclaimer

The providing institution does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or continued availability of this dataset.

The providing institution and related parties are not liable for any damage, loss, or disadvantage arising from the use of this dataset.

#### 6. Violation of Terms

If a user violates any of the license conditions, the permission to use this dataset is automatically terminated.

In such case, the user must immediately stop using this dataset.

